title: The Breakfast Club Talks With Wiz Khalifa & DJ Drama, Talks With Michael Blackson
itunes:title: The Breakfast Club Talks With Wiz Khalifa & DJ Drama, Talks With Michael Blackson
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club we got guests on guests on guests! First we air an interview between DJ Envy and Wiz Khalifa and DJ Drama. Later on during the Rumor Report we talk about Terrell Owens recent run in with a Karen. Michael Blackson also stops by to talk about all things Michael Blackson and comedy. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
